{"tid":1661400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"岑子杰呼籲別「私了」","createTime":"2019-10-18T05:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T05:25:14.000Z","uid":330873,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"89c21a7bed842b8ff1fdc493ab984b3c60113d98","tid":1661400,"uid":330873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T05:23:18.000Z","msg":"他說，身體感到痛楚，很感謝各界關心，「我看到有些人很想找到行兇者，但我覺得重點是在制度上，呢場反送中運動，不清的事情太多，究竟係邊個打我，反而係一件好小的事。831、陳彥霖發生乜嘢事？我覺得最重要是有機制、有公信力的人去還完事件真相，令大家可以信任制度。當我哋大家都唔信任制度，就會出現『私了』，用自己方式去解決，這對任何人都唔係一件好事。希望林鄭知道，香港人處於很大的恐懼和不安當中，希望她知道香港發生乜嘢事，希望香港有一個獨立調查委員會，可以重建對制度的信心。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/24254/%E5%B2%91%E5%AD%90%E6%9D%B0-%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%86-%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-24254/%E5%B2%91%E5%AD%90%E6%9D%B0%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E5%88%A5%E3%80%8C%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%86%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%9A%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E6%BA%90%E6%96%BC%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F24254%2F%25E5%25B2%2591%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%259D%25B0-%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%2586-%25E9%2581%2587%25E8%25A5%25B2-24254%2F%25E5%25B2%2591%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%259D%25B0%25E5%2591%25BC%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E5%2588%25A5%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%2586%25E3%2580%258D%25EF%25BC%259A%25E7%259C%259F%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C%25E6%25BA%2590%25E6%2596%25BC%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz4ICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=89b8cda9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/24254/%E5%B2%91%E5%AD%90%E6%9D%B0-%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%86-%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-24254/%E5%B2%91%E5%AD%90%E6%9D%B0%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E5%88%A5%E3%80%8C%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%86%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%9A%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E6%BA%90%E6%96%BC%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B</a>"},{"pid":"adfea6fcc3f5e01c0e4a0a9caa43e1c4cab24afd","tid":1661400,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T05:2